 class=\"maroon\">但到依刻多數記者唔選擇進擊</span>，<br />\n<span class=\"green\">雖然港人重會聲援及同情記者，</span><br />\n<span class=\"maroon\">然而冇人會為任何一群咁嘅人，<br />\n企係前面抵擋，直面生死危機。</span><br />\n<br />\n我同情記者今日要面對嘅<br />\n但我能夠做到亦只有咁多<br />\n唔係因為我怕死，而係當事人冇大叫「我要拼死反抗」"},{"pid":"12c25ff4807187019cb6441daa9290ebec73f69c","tid":2213749,"uid":104425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:08:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f1e2c2ed135ea9c0e41e7e56704ecb8533cbf006","tid":2213749,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85b6548085f0d8676586fbed38ceaf5a4918cae2","tid":2213749,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T18:28:13.000Z","msg":"遲下 有潘書記釋法 拍拉圖式暴動添呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:18:37.000Z","msg":"月球暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751040f7767729f9ff4a7ae113550f919aa6108c","tid":2213749,"uid":304047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:25:45.000Z","msg":"狗仔通例係狗仔自己要守<br />\n關記者/市民L事<br />\n又唔見佢地守通例<br />\n<br />\nBtw幾時加埋地球人落通例<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}